<tr>
<td style='font-size: 15px'><font color="#555555"><center><p align=justify><b>SSA</b> is a software package for the analysis of nucleic acid sequence motifs that are postionally 
correlated with a functional site such as a transcription initiation site for 
instance. The programs offered by this web server are listed below. 
</center></td>
</tr>
